            <title>[OAK-4572] Overflow to disk threshold too high</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OAK-4572</link>
                <project id="12313221" key="OAK">Jackrabbit Oak</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The overflow to disk threshold for &lt;tt&gt;StringSort&lt;/tt&gt; used by JournalEntry is too high. JournalEntry assumes the threshold is in bytes, whereas the threshold is actually the number of Strings.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
